<span id="freeTextContainer14551544642263354995"><strong>Stands the test of time</strong><br/><br/>Discovered Bruce Carton a few years ago. Read through this book (and the preceding two in the series) during the pandemic and thoroughly enjoyed them. Still good and insightful summaries of the U.S. Civil War: factually accurate and entertaining as well.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


