        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1857097430" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4188369049077399123">Excellent history of the Civil War. The key thing I learned was that Lee surrendering at Appomattox did not end the conflict. The Union had to get the other Confederate armies to surrender as well. Didn&apos;t realize that Lee wasn&apos;t in command of their entire Army. The book was also excellent due to its maps allowing the reader to follow the movements of the Armies.</span>
  <span id="freeText4188369049077399123" style="display:none">Excellent history of the Civil War. The key thing I learned was that Lee surrendering at Appomattox did not end the conflict. The Union had to get the other Confederate armies to surrender as well. Didn't realize that Lee wasn't in command of their entire Army. The book was also excellent due to its maps allowing the reader to follow the movements of the Armies.</span>
  <a data-text-id="4188369049077399123" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

